Coldwell Banker Woodland Schmidt Grand Haven

data.description: Come see this beautiful contemporary ranch home in Norton Shores! So many updates to list (all within the past 12 mo's): new hard wood & tile floors, fresh paint, new siding, updated bathrooms, new sump pump and hot water heater. In the spacious back yard you will appreciate the new fenced in yard and built in natural gas grill, perfect for your outdoor entertaining. The home also comes with a Generac (natural gas) generator for instant power for the entire home, giving you peace of mind. Upon walking into the home you will notice the spacious open concept with your kitchen, dining and living area. There's also a large family room which could be utilized for a tv room, game room, in-home office if you work remotely or a quiet sitting room overlooking the back yard. Let's not forget 3 spacious bedrooms including a generous sized primary suite and main floor laundry making this home convenient with all of your needs on one level. This home sits on a private, wooded lot and is close to Hoffmaster State Park, Lake Michigan, and all of your shopping & dining needs and is just a short distance to both 96 and 31 highways. This home provides easy access yet private enough to feel like you're away from the busyness of the city. Come see for yourself and make this your new home!
